extends ./ntu.EWR_16-17.layout.jade

block title
  title Event

block content
  .wrapper
    .poster#poster-label
      .ps-img
        //- Replace this with the poster image found in your images/org.event folder.
        img(src="../../img/16-17/ntu.EWR_16-17/EWR_16-17_background.jpg")
        .ps-cover
    .ps-well
      .col-md-3
      .col-md-6
        h1 南洋理工大学考试解压宵夜
        h3 Exam Welfare Refreshment AY 16/17 Sem1 @ NTU
        a(href="ntu.EWR_16-17.updates.html").white.btn.btn-dark.events-btn 
          h3 #活动详情
        a(href="ntu.EWR_16-17.updates.html").white.btn.btn-dark.events-btn             
          h3 #近期更新
        :markdown
          来来来，来吃来吃！民以食为天，CGPA不可以吃！所以放下书本，立志做吃货，与大家共勉。

        a(href="ntu.EWR_16-17.register.html").btn.btn-dark.btn-lg 
          h3 給我來一份!

      .col-md-3

    .container.grey-bg.full-pg#description-label
      .row
        .col-md-3
        .col-md-6
          h1.border-bottom-light 活动详情
        .col-md-3
      .row
        .col-md-4
        .col-md-5.align-left
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-clock-o.red &nbsp;
            | 活动日期 : 
            //- Replace the following date with event date
            | 3rd November 2016 
          h2 
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-calendar.yellow &nbsp;
            | 活动时间 : 
            //- Replace the following time with event time
            | 9.00 p.m. - 11 p.m.
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-building.blue &nbsp;
            | 活动地点 : 
            span.fa.fa-magic
            //- Replace the following venue with event venue 
            | TCT LT Foyer
        .col-md-3

block script
  script(type='text/javascript').
    $(document).ready(function(){
      pageScrollTo("description");
      return false;
    })